<item>
            <title>[SPR-4935] Doc: @Autowired not working in BeanFactoryPostProcessor</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-4935</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I create simple bean which implements BeanFactoryPostProcessor and has dependent bean injected with @Autowired annotation. Injection does not occur.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Workaround is to use standard XML dependency injection.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="22675">SPR-4935</key>
            <summary>Doc: @Autowired not working in BeanFactoryPostProcessor</summary>
